long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Movies Search Web is a versatile, client-centric extension that uses unique technologies to make it easier for you to find your favorite movies. Enjoy the finest cinematography with a single click. The technologies we have developed to meet your requirements are aimed at making it possible to quickly and conveniently find the best films, TV shows, news and video blogs for you. To make your experience with new tab more comfortable, we've added time and date section. Movies Search Web service provides an exceptional custom search experience powered by Microsoft Bing.

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to install "Movies Search Web" Chrome extension and hereby agree to set Chrome New Tab to that provided by the service and the Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.

You may remove this extension at any time from the chrome extension page.

Visit our website at https://moviessearchweb.com/
Read About us: https://moviessearchweb.com/about-tab/
Read our Privacy Policy: https://moviessearchweb.com/privacy-policy/
Read our Terms and Conditions: https://moviessearchweb.com/terms-conditions/
Uninstall Instructions: https://moviessearchweb.com/uninstalling-a-chrome-extension/
